{
  "stem": "25639.8",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The SS wanted to increase the volume of work, and in order to do this, they offered the French women and Polish and Danish-- these political prisoners that-- who were not Jewish-- coupons.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These coupons had a certain value, so-- so that if they completed-- finished a certain amount of work, they could get coupons valued at a certain amount.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They could then-- the inmates then could take these coupons to a little canteen-- canteen and then they could obtain or purchase food with it, drink as well.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, I never saw the canteen, but apparently it did exist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "However, the French resisted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They resisted, and they started getting beaten up by the-- the-- the SS beat them up and cussed them out-- and-- and you just don't want to work hard, you lazy bums, and accused them of all sorts of things-- for-- and--",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The French women then decided, and the others, that, why should they get beaten up?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they'll accept the coupons, but they're not going to buy anything with it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this became a-- a resistance type of movement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Actually, it became resistance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were going to-- they realized that if they are able to do more work while their stomachs have some food in it, then we, the Jews, will not be able to keep up with them.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we'll-- we'll be in a less tolerable position.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it's really an act of kindness that-- that these women have acted the way they-- they did.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They could have accepted these coupons and just cared for themselves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But no, they-- they were up to their true selves for the reasons that they were arrested and helped us, the Jewish prisoners.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
